sahodarara savaal ( kannada : ಸಹೋದರರ ಸವಾಲ ) is a 1977 indian kannada language film directed by k. s. r. das .   it stars vishnuvardhan and rajinikanth in lead roles .   it was one of the few films that rajinikanth acted in kannada .   the film was remade in telugu as annadammula savaal in 1978 starring krishna and rajinikanth .   it was dubbed into tamil as sahodara sapatham and into hindi as diller .   the kannada song hey nanagaagiye was retained in the telugu version as naakosame neevunnadhi .